  "text": "Next the case of a SC cable with core and sheath, as in Fig. 5 is considered. Original cable data from [CITATION_1] are reproduced in Table 1 . The cable arrangements are similar to those in Fig. 2b with h ¼ 0.75 m, s ¼ 0.15 m and m r ¼ 1 for all the media.",
